FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777536371
OL,3,C'I had no time with him': Grieving
OL,4,Cmother seeks answers from hospital
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FBabies born at this stage of pregnancy
OL,8,Fare considered premature and can
OL,9,Frequire specialist neonatal care, with
OL,10,Frisks including breathing difficulties
OL,11,Fand infection.
OL,13,F"They gave me all positives"
OL,15,FShe said she had been admitted to
OL,16,Fhospital with severe abdominal pain,
OL,17,Famid concerns about a previous
OL,18,Fcaesarean scar.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777536371
OL,3,C'I had no time with him': Grieving
OL,4,Cmother seeks answers from hospital
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FDoctors carried out an emergency
OL,8,Fdelivery, telling her they were
OL,9,Fprimarily concerned about her health
OL,10,Fand her baby would likely need only a
OL,11,Fshort stay in neonatal care.
OL,13,FShe said she was not informed about
OL,14,Fthe risks associated with premature
OL,15,Fbirth.
OL,17,F"They gave me all positives, we're not
OL,18,Fworried about the baby, we're worried
OL,19,Fabout you. I wish they told me the
OL,20,Ffacts, what could happen if things
OL,21,Fdidn't go the right way," she said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777536371
OL,3,C'I had no time with him': Grieving
OL,4,Cmother seeks answers from hospital
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FThe mother says she later agreed to a
OL,8,Fsterilisation procedure, which had
OL,9,Fbeen discussed during her antenatal
OL,10,Fcare, after being reassured her baby
OL,11,Fwas well.
OL,13,FHer son was taken to the neonatal unit
OL,14,Fafter birth.
OL,16,FShe says she was initially told he was
OL,17,Fdoing well, but later learned his
OL,18,Fcondition had deteriorated before his
OL,19,Fdeath - without her being informed at
OL,20,Fthe time.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777536371
OL,3,C'I had no time with him': Grieving
OL,4,Cmother seeks answers from hospital
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,F"I had no time with him"
OL,9,FShe said: "I had no time with him. I
OL,10,Fonly saw him properly after he passed
OL,11,Faway. If they'd told me he wasn't
OL,12,Fwell, I would have been there with
OL,13,Fhim."
OL,15,FThe family have raised concerns about
OL,16,Fthe standard of neonatal care,
OL,17,Fcommunication from medical staff and
OL,18,Fthe circumstances in which consent was
OL,19,Fobtained for the additional procedure.
OL,26,@qD@KOUuD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777536371
OL,3,C'I had no time with him': Grieving
OL,4,Cmother seeks answers from hospital
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FThey are also taking legal action
OL,8,Fagainst the Trust.
OL,10,FUniversity Hospitals of Leicester NHS
OL,11,FTrust is among twelve trusts being
OL,12,Fexamined as part of the nationwide
OL,13,Fmaternity review, led by Baroness
OL,14,FValerie Amos, which is looking at the
OL,15,Fsafety and quality of care provided to
OL,16,Fwomen and babies across England.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777536371
OL,3,C'I had no time with him': Grieving
OL,4,Cmother seeks answers from hospital
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FThe mother said she does not know
OL,8,Fwhether the Amos review will lead to
OL,9,Fmeaningful change, but believes
OL,10,Fimprovements are needed in the "place
OL,11,Fwe were supposed to feel safe."
OL,13,FJulie Hogg, Chief Nurse at University
OL,14,FHospitals of Leicester NHS Trust said:
OL,16,F"The safety, wellbeing and experience
OL,17,Fof women, babies and families is
OL,18,Falways our highest priority. We are
OL,19,Fsorry this family's experience of care
OL,20,Fwith us fell short of the standard we
OL,21,Fstrive to provide.
OL,26,@rD@`OUsD@_O]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777536371
OL,3,C'I had no time with him': Grieving
OL,4,Cmother seeks answers from hospital
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,F"While we cannot comment on the
OL,8,Fcircumstances of this case, we take
OL,9,Fall concerns about care extremely
OL,10,Fseriously and would welcome the
OL,11,Fopportunity to speak directly with the
OL,12,Ffamily to listen, learn and take any
OL,13,Fappropriate action."
